      "id": "PopularPost160038",
      "post_content": "I'm not gonna dvelve into the rules, but believe me this card worked. Before and after the sixth rule revolution this card say: No way you can destroy my lands! As long I keep the land untaped.  \n  \nSo use your [Icy Manipulator](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Icy Manipulator) to tap my land enchanted by Equinox and cast your [Armageddon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Armageddon) next.",
